app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online, Figure S1: Structural formula of catechin, Figure S2: 1H-NMR (METHANOL-d 4, 300 MHz) of isolated compound catechin, Figure S3: 13C-NMR (METHANOL-d 4, 75MHz of isolated compound catechin, Figure S4: EIMS of isolated compound catechin, Figure S5: FTIR spectra of isolated compound catechin, Table S1: % DPPH and ABTS free radical scavenging activity of catechin isolated from Elaeagnus umbellata fruit at various concentrations and Table S2: % α-amylase and α-glucosidase inhibition potential of catechin isolated from of Elaeagnus umbellata fruit at various concentrations.
